<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Hans Türriegel zum Riegelstein</head><p>Der Rat versichert Freundschaft wegen N. von Rüssenbach.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_283" id="141v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_283_r1l11"><expan>Hannſ<ex>en</ex></expan> Türrıgel ʒum Rıgelſtein </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_283_r1l12"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> hanns als Jr vns <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt wıe eẅch geſagt ſey daʒ wır <expan>ein<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>vnwıl<ex>len</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_283_r1l13">ʒu eẅch <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>ſull<ex>e</ex>n</expan> . von des handels <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> der ſıch von ~ des Rüſembachs </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_283_r1l14"><expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> nehſt <expan>v<ex>er</ex>loffen</expan> hat etc das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> . Vnd tun ewch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_283_r1l15">ʒu <expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> . daʒ wır eẅch von der ſache <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> keins argen <expan>gewarte<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_283_r1l16">vnd <expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> auch ʒu <expan>dıſ<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>ʒeıt<ex>en</ex></expan> mıt eẅch niht ʒu <expan>ſchık<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / Denn guts </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_283_r1l17"><expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>ſup<ex>ra</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_283" id="141v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Hanns<ex>en</ex></expan> Türrigel zum Rigelstein </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Hanns, als ir uns
                            <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt, wie ewch gesagt sey, daz wir
                                <expan>ein<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>unwil<ex>len</ex></expan> zu ewch <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>sull<ex>e</ex>n</expan> von des handels
                        <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, der sich von des Rüsembachs
                                <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> nehst
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>loffen</expan> hat, etc., das
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        und tun ewch zu <expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan>, daz wir ewch von der sache
                                <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> keins argen
                            <expan>gewarte<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, und <expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan> auch zu
                                <expan>dis<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>zeit<ex>en</ex></expan> mit ewch niht zu
                            <expan>schik<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> denn guts. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut
                                <expan>sup<ex>ra</ex></expan>. </ab>
</div>
</div></body>
